            <title>[LU-16130] Test Lustre performance using mdtest, error when following mdtest wiki. </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16130</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are trying to test the lustre performance for DOM after making some changes to our current environment.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When attempting to follow steps provided on mdtest wiki i am getting the below error for rhel 7 o/s system on the MGS server.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;playpen_server ior-3.3.0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;$ module load mpi/openmpi-x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;playpen_server ior-3.3.0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;$ make clean &amp;amp;&amp;amp; make&lt;br/&gt;
make: *** No rule to make target `clean&apos;. &#160;Stop.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you please advise on how to resolve this problem or is there some other way i can test the DOM performance?&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Downloaded zip file from &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/hpc/ior/releases&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Releases &#183; hpc/ior &#183; GitHub.&#160;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
